---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Aethel_AI — smart tools for everyday life.">
  <div class="page">
    <div class="container">
      <article class="page__content">
        <h1 class="page__title">About Aethel_AI</h1>
        <p>
          Welcome to <strong>Aethel_AI</strong> — a space where we explore how smart tools can make everyday life easier, faster, and more fun. No complicated jargon. No technical deep dives. Just clear, practical advice.
        </p>
        <p>
          We started this blog because we noticed something: the most powerful productivity tools on the planet were being talked about in ways that made them sound complicated or intimidating. The tech industry loves buzzwords. We don't.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our mission is simple: <em>help people use modern tools without needing a computer science degree.</em> Whether it's turning voice memos into documents, having software organize your calendar, or automating the boring repetitive tasks that eat up your week — we cover it all in plain language.
        </p>
        <h2>Why the name "Aethel"?</h2>
        <p>
          "Aethel" is an Old English word meaning "noble" or "excellent." It's the root of names like Ethan and Athelstan. We chose it because it reflects our belief that using smart tools isn't about replacing human ability — it's about elevating it. Doing excellent work without the busywork.
        </p>
        <h2>What you'll find here</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Practical guides</strong> — step-by-step walkthroughs for real tasks</li>
          <li><strong>Tool comparisons</strong> — honest looks at what works and what doesn't</li>
          <li><strong>Workflow ideas</strong> — ways to save time you hadn't thought of</li>
          <li><strong>No hype</strong> — just what actually works</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page {
    padding: var(--space-16) 0 var(--space-24);
  }

  .page__content {
    max-width: var(--content-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .page__title {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .page__content p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
  }

  .page__content h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-10);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  .page__content ul {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    padding-left: var(--space-6);
  }

  .page__content li {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
  }
</style>
